    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a concours-level example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically superlative, the VANOS system has been completely overhauled, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. The factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional lockup, while the suspension retains its original dampening profile with zero bushing play. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, the exterior remains in showroom state with original paint depth and no road rash. A fully documented service history confirms rigorous maintenance of the 8,000 RPM valvetrain. Turnkey and ready for the most discerning enthusiast.",
